### Version
2.5.17

### Reproduction link
[https://jsfiddle.net/eywraw8t/281722/](https://jsfiddle.net/eywraw8t/281722/)





### Steps to reproduce
* Register a component , by directive or methods to change `this.$el.parentNode`
* Put the component behind the v-for list
```
<template>
  <div>
    <div v-for="item in arr">{{item}}</div>
    <com />
  </div>
</template>
```

### What is expected?
list render

### What is actually happening?
```
function insert (parent, elm, ref) {
    if (isDef(parent)) {
      if (isDef(ref)) {
        // ref.parentNode has been changed，insertBefore can't execute.
        if (ref.parentNode === parent) {
          nodeOps.insertBefore(parent, elm, ref)
        }
      } else {
        nodeOps.appendChild(parent, elm)
      }
    }
  }
```

